{"tid":1545354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大西北牛牛真係好衰，撞爛黨鐵27部售票機、194部八達通收費器、3個乘客資訊顯示屏、38部閉路電視及7個廣告板","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:24:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e8a77e5661b8a0412532c7c140675012f19273","tid":1545354,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"牛牛知唔知售票機好貴呀，新機幾十萬一部，肉都赤埋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新版發達通收費器幾萬一部，爛咗唔防水好易出煙，好危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乘客顯示屏係德國定瑞士製，絕晒版無零件。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老閉又要用梯換，行車時間可能唔換得，要等收車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190906/s00001/1567708051323/%e5%af%b6%e7%90%b3%e7%ab%99%e9%81%87%e8%a5%b2%e4%bc%91%e7%8f%ad%e7%ab%99%e9%95%b78-31%e9%81%ad%e9%bb%9e%e7%9b%b8-%e8%bb%8a%e5%bb%82%e5%85%a7%e9%9b%99%e6%96%b9%e6%8b%89%e6%89%af-%e8%ad%a6%e6%8b%98%e5%85%a9%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190906%2Fs00001%2F1567708051323%2F%25e5%25af%25b6%25e7%2590%25b3%25e7%25ab%2599%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e4%25bc%2591%25e7%258f%25ad%25e7%25ab%2599%25e9%2595%25b78-31%25e9%2581%25ad%25e9%25bb%259e%25e7%259b%25b8-%25e8%25bb%258a%25e5%25bb%2582%25e5%2585%25a7%25e9%259b%2599%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%258b%2589%25e6%2589%25af-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%258b%2598%25e5%2585%25a9%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=770dab68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190906%2Fs00001%2F1567708051323%2F%25e5%25af%25b6%25e7%2590%25b3%25e7%25ab%2599%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e4%25bc%2591%25e7%258f